{"tid":2286736,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《夜更》奪大獎  導演「面對糟糕嘅香港」","createTime":"2020-11-15T08:33:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-15T13:52:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ee84af2091ef8af9dd8767321095caa8d48705ba","tid":2286736,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:33:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201115/ZOGV6LGCPVHMJDWXOXYV3N3AFQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201115%2FZOGV6LGCPVHMJDWXOXYV3N3AFQ%2F&d=eSah%2B3q63CE7QW%2BLxhD4%2BBQiWlS3rEx2Iifn9b7K3wo%3D&h=a65e7fc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201115%2FZOGV6LGCPVHMJDWXOXYV3N3AFQ%2F&h=413c1210\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201115/ZOGV6LGCPVHMJDWXOXYV3N3AFQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n《夜更》奪大獎 <br />\n導演「面對糟糕嘅香港」<br />\n<br />\n電影《十年》中執導《浮瓜》一章的導演郭臻，近日再次執導短片《夜更》先後入圍今屆金馬獎最佳劇情短片及2020年南方影展最佳劇情短片，《夜更》前日率先在南方影展打響勝鼓，拿下大獎。郭臻戴上黃色口罩，以視像接受南方影展得獎訪問，先以普通話多謝評審支持，其後特別以廣東話發言：「呢部片屬於舊年遇過嘅每一個香港人。係佢哋話我知，做香港人係可以有啲嘢proud of（值得驕傲）。」<br />\n<br />\n郭臻又指希望《夜更》可以幫助香港人釋放情緒，但又提醒：「回憶起舊年嘅自己係點樣，唔好忘記我哋憤怒，唔好忘記我哋付出好多，犧牲好多嘅手足們。無論時勢好壞，希望我哋可以攞出勇氣去面對呢個更加糟糕嘅香港。keep fighting. 」然後分別做出用手遮掩右眼及五一手勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yo9pat1DyAd5JCbemplMf99q5YY=/640x800/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RSLMWT75QZG5ZKKXPRNDAY55HM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fyo9pat1DyAd5JCbemplMf99q5YY%3D%2F640x800%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRSLMWT75QZG5ZKKXPRNDAY55HM.jpg&h=9a458f4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■郭臻（圖）前晚以視像談得獎感受，希望《夜更》能助港人釋放情緒。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/7Juw5wC9aquSUr0pFLen_Q2tFzk=/640x420/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MNO53VB4E5BZ5JS2GZDRZ65OZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F7Juw5wC9aquSUr0pFLen_Q2tFzk%3D%2F640x420%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMNO53VB4E5BZ5JS2GZDRZ65OZI.jpg&h=55fa8c2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《夜更》劇照"},{"pid":"d75a495e8f7d2e7e81ad49e3ba17ec16b1e62417","tid":2286736,"uid":24862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"177034bee79397ab5d6f9bf1d16a87247f7c94ec","tid":2286736,"uid":240004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:43:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8926f32208dd158b69de3e73227ea4d2c826876a","tid":2286736,"uid":44874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"792d963d3cd66f45acb21ce62db8bef6b585ab30","tid":2286736,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:52:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b223a6a4b5685031c747525531b0e2dffae7b23","tid":2286736,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8926f32208dd158b69de3e73227ea4d2c826876a","tid":2286736,"uid":44874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T08:45:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sn